Ekigambo kya Katonda, Bayibuli, egamba nti Katonda atuwadde ekigambo kye ekituyaamba okuba na buli kyetwetaaga okukola emirimu emirungi.
Ekigambo kitusomesa engeri y'okukkiriza na kki eky'okukkiriza, kitubikkulira amakubo amakyamu getuba tulonze, era nekituyaamba okudda mu Kkubo ettuufu, n’okulinywererakko, Abaebbulaniya 4:12 etugamba nti ekigambo kya Katonda kiramu, kyamanyi era kisobola okuyingira emitima gyaffe okusigukulayo n'okuwangula ebibi ebikyasinze okukwekebwa ewala.
Omuwandiisi wa Zabbuli ayogera ku manyi g'ekigambo agakyuusa obulamu mu Zabbuli 119.
