Sitaani ne zi dayimooni ze kakano zinonya kulemesa oba kwonoona mirimu gya Katonda era okulimba buli gwezisobola okulimba (1 Peteero 5:8; 2 Abakkolinso 11:14-15 ).
(1 Timoseewo 4:1) egilumba abakristaayo (2 Abakkolinso 12:7; 1 Petero 5:8), era egilwanyisa bamalayika abatukuvu (Okubikkulirwa 12:4-9).
“kubanga ali mu mmwe asinga obukulu ali mu nsi.” (Yokaana 4:4).
