Bayibuli terina wegaana kukozesa ebirabo by'omwoyo omutukuvu (1 Abakolinso 12).
Abasajja balina okubeera eky’okulabirako mu bukulembeze—okuyita mu bulamu bwabwe era n'ebigambo byabwe.
( Abagalatiya 5:22-23), era n'okubulira enjiri eri abaabula( Matayo 28: 18-20; Ebikolwa 1:8; 1 Petero 3;15).
